{"tid":1472391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋唔應該再叫警察做狗","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:58:37.000Z","uid":295867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf80daea66f771e1d1f35413f8239f5b4439f6ec","tid":1472391,"uid":295867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"好多人之前都有講，其實佢地已經對狗呢個叫法冇乜感覺，至於黑社會，強姦犯只會令佢地更有認同感，我哋係時候要升級！<br />\n<br />\n狗係人類嘅朋友，侮辱性其實真係唔夠高，要用低等生物、害蟲黎稱呼佢地，而且仲要無時無刻都用呢個稱呼！<br />\n<br />\n以其人之道還其人之身<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曱甴</span></span><br />\n<br />\n又或者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老鼠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n又或者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屎蟲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再唔係反正都唔知係唔係武警扮嘅，直接叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蝗蟲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n淨係諗到呢幾樣，大家一齊brainstorm下"},{"pid":"53885e7ba0fa9170d0f64ee017eb461f6b2002ca","tid":1472391,"uid":171992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupl